            list in a selectbox to choose from.
          </p>
          <a href="screenshots/listdialog.png">
              <img src="screenshots/listdialog-small.png"/>
          </a>
          <p>
            The document is created in the conference-folder.
          </p>
          <a href="screenshots/eventdocument.png">
              <img src="screenshots/eventdocument.png"/>
          </a>
        </subsection>
      </section>
